quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,Suferinta catre every backbiter slanderer
  104,2,El pastra bani socoti el
  104,3,As daca his bani produce him imortabil
  104,4,Niciodata; el arunca Devastator
  104,5,Tu sti care Devastator Do exista
  104,6,Dumnezeu arde Hellfire
  104,7,El arde ele complet
  104,8,Ei limita therein
  104,9,În extended coloana